            <h3>FORENSICS ANALYSIS</h3>
            <P>Forensic analysis in cybersecurity is like being a digital detective. When something suspicious happens—like a data breach or hack—experts investigate what went wrong, how it happened, and who did it. They collect evidence, trace digital footprints, and help businesses understand the attack so it doesn’t happen again.
            </P>
